---
import BaseThemeLayout from '@layouts/BaseThemeLayout.astro';
---

<BaseThemeLayout
  ogImage="/ogImageLandscape__The-Water-Foundation.jpg"
  ogImagePortrait="/ogImagePortrait__The-Water-Foundation.jpg"
  title="Investor Board - The Water Foundation"
  description="Investment strategy, portfolio oversight, and financial governance for sustainable returns."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-b from-background to-background/50">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-24 md:pb-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 via-emerald-500 to-teal-600 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extralight text-white mb-6 tracking-wider leading-tight">Investor Board</h1>
        <div class="w-32 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white to-transparent mx-auto mb-8 opacity-60"></div>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed font-light">
          Investment strategy, portfolio oversight, and financial governance for sustainable returns.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
          <h2 class="water-header">Mission & Scope</h2>
          <p>
            The Investor Board oversees our investment strategy and portfolio management, ensuring that 
            capital deployment aligns with our mission while generating sustainable returns for stakeholders.
          </p>

          <h2 class="water-header">Investment Philosophy</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose">
            <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Impact-First Investing</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Prioritizing measurable water impact while maintaining financial sustainability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Long-term Value Creation</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Building sustainable businesses that create lasting value for all stakeholders.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Risk-Adjusted Returns</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Balancing impact objectives with prudent risk management and return expectations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-card p-6 rounded-lg border">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-primary">Portfolio Diversification</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Spreading investments across technologies, geographies, and development stages.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="water-header">Key Responsibilities</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Investment strategy development and implementation</li>
            <li>Portfolio company oversight and value creation</li>
            <li>Due diligence and investment committee decisions</li>
            <li>Risk management and portfolio optimization</li>
            <li>Investor relations and capital raising</li>
            <li>Exit strategy planning and execution</li>
            <li>Performance monitoring and reporting</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="water-header">Investment Focus Areas</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 not-prose">
            <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Water Technology Ventures</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Early to growth-stage companies developing innovative water solutions.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Infrastructure Projects</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Large-scale water infrastructure investments in emerging markets.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-4 border-primary pl-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-primary mb-2">Blended Finance Initiatives</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Combining commercial and philanthropic capital for maximum impact.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="water-header">Investment Process</h2>
          <p>
            Our investment process combines rigorous financial analysis with comprehensive impact assessment, 
            ensuring that every investment contributes to our mission while meeting return expectations.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-primary/10 p-6 rounded-lg not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-primary">Investment Criteria</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-muted-foreground">
              <li>• Clear path to water impact at scale</li>
              <li>• Strong management team and business model</li>
              <li>• Competitive advantage and market opportunity</li>
              <li>• Alignment with ESG principles</li>
              <li>• Appropriate risk-return profile</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <h2 class="water-header">Board Composition</h2>
          <p>
            Our Investor Board includes experienced investment professionals, water industry experts, 
            and impact investing specialists with proven track records in building successful portfolios.
          </p>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-6 not-prose">
            <div class="bg-card p-8 rounded-lg border">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
                <img 
                  src="/headshots/headshotOf__Laura-Wasserson.webp" 
                  alt="Laura Wasserson" 
                  class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full object-cover flex-shrink-0"
                />
                <div>
                  <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-primary">Laura Wasserson</h3>
                  <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-4 font-medium">Investor Board Member</p>
                  <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Laura Wasserson brings extensive expertise in ESG and climate finance with a career spanning the United Nations and Nasdaq. 
                    At Nasdaq, she served as Head of Carbon Strategy and ESG Advisory, leading initiatives to embed carbon procurement and 
                    climate risk into corporate value chains. She is a Partner at Wild Assets, an investor with Investors for Climate, 
                    and serves on the board of Sinkco Labs. Laura's expertise in carbon markets, ESG integration, and impact investment 
                    drives transformative solutions at the intersection of water, climate, and finance.
                  </p>
                  <div class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
                    <a href="https://x.com/LauraMetalplant" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
                      </svg>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/laurawasserson/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">
                      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
                      </svg>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-muted/50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-6">
            <p class="text-center text-muted-foreground italic">
              Additional board member profiles will be available soon.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseThemeLayout>
